{"tid":2256413,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【又係你  大和田】美海岸防衛隊西太平洋設巡防艦　反制中國非法捕魚活動","createTime":"2020-10-24T10:37:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T13:08:51.000Z","uid":54337,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7f072a63034caca929372d6b80f93e9dbfe96980","tid":2256413,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T10:37:02.000Z","msg":"美海岸防衛隊西太平洋設巡防艦 反制中國非法捕魚活動<br />\n<br />\n美國國安顧問奧布萊恩（Robert O'Brien）周五（23日）表示，美國海岸防衛隊將在西太平洋部署巡防艦執行海上安全任務，以打擊中國在該海域的非法、未經管制的捕魚活動。<br />\n<br />\n奧布萊恩批評中國對其他國家的漁船造成騷擾，危及區域穩定，美國海岸防衛隊將部署新一代快速反應巡防艦（Fast Response Cutters），在西太平洋執行海上安全任務，包括近海監視、與執法能力有限的區域合作伙伴協作及幫助漁船，確保航行自由。<br />\n<br />\n奧布萊恩亦稱，海岸防衛隊正評估在美屬薩摩亞永久部署巡邏船的可行性，若然成事將有助美國進一步深入南太平洋。"},{"pid":"368624de1548f6d4e7f369a144f57d3c96da1dcb","tid":2256413,"uid":54337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T10:37:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20201024/s00005/1603520765912/%E7%BE%8E%E6%B5%B7%E5%B2%B8%E9%98%B2%E8%A1%9B%E9%9A%8A%E8%A5%BF%E5%A4%AA%E5%B9%B3%E6%B4%8B%E8%A8%AD%E5%B7%A1%E9%98%B2%E8%89%A6-%E5%8F%8D%E5%88%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E6%8D%95%E9%AD%9A%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20201024%2Fs00005%2F1603520765912%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25B2%25B8%25E9%2598%25B2%25E8%25A1%259B%25E9%259A%258A%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%25B4%258B%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E5%25B7%25A1%25E9%2598%25B2%25E8%2589%25A6-%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%2588%25B6%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%258D%2595%25E9%25AD%259A%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%258B%2595&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLCC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=a2af58ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20201024%2Fs00005%2F1603520765912%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25B2%25B8%25E9%2598%25B2%25E8%25A1%259B%25E9%259A%258A%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%25B4%258B%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E5%25B7%25A1%25E9%2598%25B2%25E8%2589%25A6-%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%2588%25B6%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%258D%2595%25E9%25AD%259A%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%258B%2595&h=830e39e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20201024/s00005/1603520765912/%E7%BE%8E%E6%B5%B7%E5%B2%B8%E9%98%B2%E8%A1%9B%E9%9A%8A%E8%A5%BF%E5%A4%AA%E5%B9%B3%E6%B4%8B%E8%A8%AD%E5%B7%A1%E9%98%B2%E8%89%A6-%E5%8F%8D%E5%88%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E6%8D%95%E9%AD%9A%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95</a>"},{"pid":"5a2a52436fcba3586ad4be6c4f82e9ed6478602f","tid":2256413,"uid":231583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T10:37:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4e4ba485ee1c779391a27ab546ccadc9c090ce4","tid":2256413,"uid":54337,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T10:38:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KcjhcVw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKcjhcVw.gif&h=34aba30e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JVZkU80.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJVZkU80.gif&h=ec2d2ffc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0feb7afc79ca5a10fbc4509f5da158067f49cae7","tid":2256413,"uid":158270,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T10:40:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ezpUe9D.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FezpUe9D.gif&h=81914b4e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb2d84e874b88a0a01def2db89982731d1fbe524","tid":2256413,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T10:40:48.000Z","msg":"打擊中國漁船騷擾 美部署巡防艦守西太平洋<br />\n<br />\n美國國家安全顧問奧布賴恩周五（23日）說，為了打擊中國非法捕魚及騷擾印太地區的漁船，美國海岸防衞隊已決定在西太平洋部署新一代快速反應巡防艦，執行海上安全任務。<br />\n奧布賴恩在聲明批評，中國非法、未經報告及不受管制的捕魚行為，以及騷擾印太其他國家專屬經濟區的船隻，威脅美國及太平洋鄰國主權，破壞區內穩定。他說，美國作為太平洋強國，包括海岸防衞隊在內的政府部門，努力應對這些破壞穩定及惡劣行為。<br />\n他續指，海岸防衞隊會繼續現代化和加強巡防艦隊的能力，保護美國重要國家利益與區內的盟友利益，因此部署新一代快速反應巡防艦，在西太平洋執行海上安全任務，包括漁業巡防及近海監視，以及與執法能力有限的區域夥伴合作，確保區內航行自由。他又說，海岸防衞隊計劃在2021財政年度，評估在美屬薩摩亞部署這種巡防艦的可行性；如果調查結果正面，美國可能將任務進一步擴大至南太平洋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20201024/mobile/bkn-20201024100359229-1024_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20201024%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20201024100359229-1024_00952_001.html&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLCC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=559911a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20201024/mobile/bkn-20201024100359229-1024_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4c16b23912ab9b35a4fce9bda027b42965a97db7","tid":2256413,"uid":287422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d4e4ba485ee1c779391a27ab546ccadc9c090ce4","tid":2256413,"uid":54337,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T10:38:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KcjhcVw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKcjhcVw.gif&h=34aba30e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JVZkU80.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJVZkU80.gif&h=ec2d2ffc&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T10:41:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b759e0ca2c0923babc3b00ef2f4c94a766e99c6b","tid":2256413,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T10:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" c